{
  "stem": "4284.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I have the conviction that, given any opportunity that people are willing to take with nobody safeguarding, this is not an isolated incident.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Right now, well, we'll see this in the future, might hear about Bosnia, Herzegovina, Rwanda.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "People will let it happen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's the only message.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's the only message anybody can give to anybody who cares to listen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because people all over the world, whether it's Nazis or whether it's anybody else, if they believe that they can get away with something that's inhumane and serves their purpose, there will be countries, there will be people, there will be circumstances that will allow it to happen.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And whether it's by education, or common sense, or by any kind of ideology, this is not something that was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's something that currently is, and inevitably, sometime in the future will be again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the message is to be on guard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You have a freedom, in this country at least, that allows you the freedom of speech, freedom of thought.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But it must be directed in a constructive manner, not in idiotic, fanatical, and unreasonable things without some checks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the problem is that we have different societies.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We have different philosophies.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And if some minority, in most cases, feels that there is a way to get away with it, they will at least try.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And if you have enough people that will adhere to this with no safeguard, no police, no court, no judges opposing it because they believe in this false ideology, it will get out of hand.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it will repeat itself throughout history time and time again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You're very welcome.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
